": "It's a big music video day for Bruce: in Berlin, he teams up with Wolfgang Niedecken for a new \"Hungry Heart\" video, in Sheffield he shoots the official \"Spare Parts\" video, and on the Internet, he releases the short film, \"Hunter of Invisible Game.\"", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/bba81.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/bba81.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/bba81.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/bba81.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/bba81.jpg?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 15842, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2020/02/02/roll-of-the-dice-heavens-wall/", "url_meta": {"origin": 7408, "position": 2}, "title": "Roll of the Dice: Heaven&#8217;s Wall", "author": "Ken", "date": "February 2, 2020", "format": false, "excerpt": "Who the heck would ever think to combine samba rhythm, middle eastern melody, a self-guitar duel, discordant strings, cowbell, and a gospel choir? Bruce Springsteen, that's who!", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Roll of the Dice&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Roll of the Dice", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/roll-of-the-dice/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/heaven.jpg?fit=1024%2C768&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/heaven.jpg?fit=1024%2C768&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/heaven.jpg?fit=1024%2C768&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/heaven.jpg?fit=1024%2C768&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 57724, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/07/16/kingdom-of-days-july-16-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 7408, "position": 3}, "title": "July 16", "author": "Ken", "date": "July 16, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Bruce kicks off a magical show at Circus Maximus with \"New York City Serenade\" (complete with strings), plays a one-time-only cover of \"Honky Tonk,\" and makes surprise appearances at Jersey shore bar gigs. More highlights inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/rome16.webp?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/rome16.webp?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/rome16.webp?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/rome16.webp?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/rome16.webp?fit=1200%2C1200&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 58379, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/16/kingdom-of-days-august-16-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 7408, "position": 4}, "title": "August 16", "author": "Ken", "date": "August 16, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: Earth makes their public debut, Bruce premieres \"Sea Cruise,\" \"It's Gonna Work Out Fine,\" 